|--------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------|
| *First-<br>Person*     | [#[First-person singular for masculine singular noun|סִפְרִי<br>_sifri_<br>“My sefer”]]            |  \<      | [#[First-person plural for masculine singular noun|סִפְרֵינוּ<br>_sifraynu_<br>“Our sefer”]]      |  \<      |
| *Second-<br>Person*    | [#[Second-person masculine singular for masculine singular noun|סִפְרְךָ<br>_sif’r’chah_<br>“Your sefer” (man)]] | [#[Second-person feminine singular for masculine singular noun|סִפְרֵךְ<br>_sifraych_<br>“Your sefer” (woman)]] | [#[Second-person masculine plural for masculine singular noun|סִפְרְכֶם<br>_sif’r’chchem_<br>“Your sefer” (men)]] | [#[Second-person feminine plural for masculine singular noun|סִפְרְכֶן<br>_sif’r’chen_<br>“Your sefer” (women)]] |
| *Third-<br>Person*     | [#[Third-person masculine singular for masculine singular noun|סִפְרוֹ<br>_sifro_<br>“His sefer”]]          | [#[Third-person feminine singular for masculine singular noun|סִפְרָהּ<br>_sifroh_<br>“Her sefer”]]          | [#[Third-person masculine plural for masculine singular noun|סִפְרָם<br>_sifrom_<br>“Their sefer” (men)]]        | [#[Third-person feminine plural for masculine singular noun|סִפְרָן<br>_sifron_<br>“Their sefer” (women)]]         |

