* Kiddushin 41a:
Kiddushin 41a [[(image)]] is composed of the following sections: <small>{{[[Kiddushin 41a/Mishnah Haish Mekadesh|(Start with Mishnah)]]}}</small>
| *Kiddushin 41a*  | \< | \< |
| <small>{{[[Tosofos {41a:1 |}D"H _hashta bshlucho_]]}}</small> | [![End of the first perek]] | [![Rashi on previous perek]] |
| <small>{{[[Tosofos {41a:2 |}D"H _e itmar dRav<br> Yosef asefia itmar_]]}}</small> | [[{{Mishnah }} of<br>{{_ha’ish mekadesh_}}]] | [[Rashi on {|the }Mishnah {Haish Mekadesh|}]] |
| <small>{{[[Tosofos {41a:3 |}D"H _asur ladam<br> shyekadesh isha v’chulu_]]}}</small> | [[Gemara of<br>{{_hashta b’shlucho_}}]] | [[Rashi on _hashta b’shlucho_]] |
| <small>{{[[Tosofos {41a:4 |}D"H _k’sh’hi na’ara<br> in k’sh’hi katana lo_]]}}</small> | [[Gemara of<br>{{_k’sh’hi na’ara in_}}]] | \^ |
| <small>{{[[Tosofos {41a:5 |}D"H _asur l’adam<br>sh’yikadesh es bito<br>k’sh’hi katana_]]}}</small> | \^ | \^ |
| \^ | [![Gemara of _shlichus menalan_]] | [![Rashi on _k’sh’hi na’ara in_]] |
| <small>{{[![Tosofos D"H _v’shalach_]]}}</small> | \^ | [![Rashi on _shlichus menalan_]] |
| <small>{{[![Tosofos D"H _torem k’daas ba’al habayis_]]}}</small> | \< | \< |
